Sazka Bankruptcy Affirmed by Appeals Court, Hospodarske Reports

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-07-21T06:34:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/sazka-bankruptcy-affirmed-by-appeals-court-hospodarske-reports.html
Sazka AS’s bankruptcy was affirmed
by an appeals court yesterday, giving control over the Czech
lottery company to its biggest creditors, PPF Group NV and KKCG,
Hospodarske Noviny  reported , citing the court’s ruling.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  